properties.tooltip:
Environment variables injected into the sandbox. Format: JSON object.

Examples:
{"API_KEY": "my-key", "DEBUG": "true"}

For secrets, use Camunda secrets syntax:
{"API_KEY": "{{secrets.MY_API_KEY}}"}

Cloud CLI credentials (if not pre-configured):
{"AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID": "{{secrets.AWS_KEY}}", "AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY": "{{secrets.AWS_SECRET}}"}

Variables are isolated to this execution only.
